'''2019年环意自行车赛'''是第102届[[环意自行车赛|环意自行车赛]]，于2019年5月11日至6月2日进行，此次比赛是2019年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-worldtour-calendar-for-2019/|title=UCI reveal WorldTour calendar for 2019|work=Cycling News|date=2018-06-15|accessdate=2018-12-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913120245/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-worldtour-calendar-for-2019/|archivedate=2020-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛的起点位于[[博洛尼亚|博洛尼亚]]，终点位于[[维罗纳|维罗纳]]，除第九赛段途经[[圣马力诺|圣马力诺]]外，其余比赛路线均在意大利境内<ref name="CW1">{{cite news|url=https://www.cyclingweekly.com/news/racing/giro-ditalia/giro-ditalia-route-192184|title=Giro d'Italia 2019 route: Seven summit finishes and three individual time trials in all-Italian route|work=Cycling Weekly|first1=Gregor|last1=Brown|first2=Alex|last2=Ballinger|date=2018-10-31|accessdate=2018-12-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220230320/https://www.cyclingweekly.com/news/racing/giro-ditalia/giro-ditalia-route-192184|archivedate=2018-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

总共有来自22支车队的176名自行车手参加此次比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/cycling/2019/05/10/giro-ditalia-2019-predictions-six-riders-think-may-win/|title=Giro d'Italia 2019 predictions: Who are the six riders we think may win?|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2019-05-10|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510063421/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/cycling/2019/05/10/giro-ditalia-2019-predictions-six-riders-think-may-win/|archivedate=2019-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自移动之星车队的[[理察·卡拉帕斯|理察·卡拉帕斯]]获得此次比赛的总冠军，成为历史上首位赢得环意自行车赛总冠军的厄瓜多尔选手<ref name="AP NEWS">{{cite news |title=Carapaz wins Giro d'Italia, Haga clinches final stage |url=https://apnews.com/f6abfd83f2ff46e893f8f758aa3ae465 |accessdate=2019-06-02 |work=AP NEWS |date=2019-06-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602213511/https://apnews.com/f6abfd83f2ff46e893f8f758aa3ae465 |archivedate=2019-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/cycling/48489871 |title=Giro d'Italia: Richard Carapaz becomes the first Ecuadorian and to win the Giro d'Italia |work=[[BBC体育|BBC Sport]] |date=2019-06-02 |accessdate=2019-06-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603130423/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/cycling/48489871 |archivedate=2019-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及历史上第二位赢得环意自行车赛总冠军的南美洲选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20190602-carapaz-triumphs-giro-italia-cycling-ecuador-nibali|title=Carapaz triumphs in Giro d'Italia, first Ecuadorian to win a Grand Tour|publisher=France 24|date=2019-06-02|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927001627/https://www.france24.com/en/20190602-carapaz-triumphs-giro-italia-cycling-ecuador-nibali|archivedate=2020-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自巴林–美利达车队的意大利车手[[溫琴佐·尼巴利|溫琴佐·尼巴利]]获得第二名，而来自[[Jumbo–Visma车队|Jumbo–Visma车队]]的斯洛文尼亚车手[[普里莫日·羅格里奇|普里莫日·羅格里奇]]则位列总成绩榜第三名。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ostanek |first1=Daniel |title=Richard Carapaz wins the 2019 Giro d'Italia |url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/giro-ditalia-2019/stage-21/results/ |accessdate=2019-06-02 |work=cyclingnews.com |date=2019-06-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906182600/https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/giro-ditalia-2019/stage-21/results/ |archivedate=2020-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

